text: Hana Zagorová (6 September 1946 – 26 August 2022) was a Czech singer- songwriter, actress, and presenter. She won the national Zlatý slavík music award, nine times between 1977 and 1985.Hana Zagorova , a profile at the Český Slavík website ==References== Category:1946 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Czech singer-songwriters Category:Czech movie actors
